edu.ucla.sspace.temporal

Class FileBasedTemporalSemanticSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.temporal.FileBasedTemporalSemanticSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticSpace, TemporalSemanticSpace

    public class FileBasedTemporalSemanticSpace
extends Object
implements TemporalSemanticSpace
    A TemporalSemanticSpace created from the serialized output of another TemporalSemanticSpace after it has finished processing. The input format of the file should be one of the formats specified by TSSpaceFormat.
    See Also:
    TemporalSemanticSpaceUtils
